            &lt;div dir=3D&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Hello list,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;TL;DR: the core opcodes of =
MATT can build vaults with a very similar design&lt;br&gt;to OP_VAULT. Code examp=
le here:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=3D&quot;https://github.com/bitcoin-inquisition/bitcoin/=
